<p>打开终端，使用 ssh-keygen 工具生成 SSH 私钥（<a href="https://docs.github.com/cn/authentication/connecting-to-github-with-ssh/generating-a-new-ssh-key-and-adding-it-to-the-ssh-agent" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreffer">GitHub 推荐方法</a>）：</p>
