</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Generating public/private ecdsa key pair.
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Enter file in which to save the key <span class="o">(</span>/home/kwang/.ssh/id_ecdsa<span class="o">)</span>: /home/kwang/.ssh/id_ecdsa
